# Campusly — The Campus Economy

> One platform. Every need on campus.

[![CI](https://github.com/campusly/campusly/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/campusly/campusly/actions/workflows/ci.yml)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-UNLICENSED-blue)](LICENSE)

Campusly is a trusted, closed-ecosystem super-app built for university campuses — where students buy, sell, earn, collaborate, eat, and connect, all within a verified student community.

## 🚀 Core Modules

| Module | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Marketplace** | Buy & sell second-hand goods with escrow protection |
| **SkillHub** | Freelance services & collaboration |
| **RunIt** | Errands & convenience tasks |
| **CampusEats** | Food & beverage delivery |
| **QuickGigs** | Micro-jobs & task board |
| **CampusConnect** | Events, teams & community |
| **CampusWallet** | Payments & financial layer |

